info.description:
Web based photo album, family movies streaming, personal music collection
cataloging and online player. Blogging system, file system web browser interface
and more.
        
Requires:             
      1. webware - http://www.webwareforpython.org/
      2. mxDateTime - http://www.egenix.com/files/python/
      3. elementtree - http://effbot.org/zone/element-index.htm
      4. PIL - http://www.pythonware.com/products/pil/index.htm
